### 1. 注册用户
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Leanne",
  "lastName": "Graham",
  "username": "leanne",
  "password": "password",
  "email": "leanne.graham@gmail.com"
}

### 2. 登录获取JWT令牌
# @name login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "leanne",
  "password": "password"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.accessToken);
    client.global.set("current_username", response.body.username);
%}

### 3. 检查用户名可用性
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/checkUsernameAvailability?username=testuser

### 4. 检查邮箱可用性
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/checkEmailAvailability?email=test@example.com

