### ============================
### 博客文章相关API
### ============================

### 15. 获取所有文章
GET http://localhost:8080/api/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 16. 获取指定ID的文章
GET http://localhost:8080/api/posts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 17. 创建文章
# @name createPost
POST http://localhost:8080/api/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "sunt aut facere repellat provident occaecati excepturi optio reprehenderit",
  "body": "quia et suscipit suscipit recusandae consequuntur expedita et cum reprehenderit molestiae ut ut quas totam nostrum rerum est autem sunt rem eveniet architecto"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("post_id", response.body.id);
%}

### 18. 更新文章
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/posts/{{post_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "UPDATED TITLE",
  "body": "UPDATED CONTENT UPDATED CONTENT UPDATED CONTENT"
}

### 19. 删除文章
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/posts/{{post_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### ============================
### 评论相关API
### ============================

### 20. 获取文章的所有评论
GET http://localhost:8080/api/posts/{{post_id}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 21. 创建评论
# @name createComment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/posts/{{post_id}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "laudantium enim quasi est quidem magnam voluptate ipsam eos tempora quo necessitatibus dolor quam autem quasi reiciendis et nam sapiente accusantium"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("comment_id", response.body.id);
%}

### 22. 获取指定评论
GET http://localhost:8080/api/posts/{{post_id}}/comments/{{comment_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 23. 更新评论
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/posts/{{post_id}}/comments/{{comment_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "UPDATED COMMENT UPDATED COMMENT UPDATED COMMENT"
}

### 24. 删除评论
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/posts/{{post_id}}/comments/{{comment_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

