### 39. 更新待办事项
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/todos/{{todo_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "delectus aut autem Updated",
  "completed": true
}

### 40. 删除待办事项
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/todos/{{todo_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 41. 标记待办事项为完成
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/todos/{{todo_id}}/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 42. 标记待办事项为未完成
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/todos/{{todo_id}}/unComplete
